                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |                                 TableScan: catalog_sales projection=[cs_sold_date_sk, cs_item_sk, cs_order_number, cs_quantity, cs_ext_sales_price]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           